Package: siorb
Version: @VERSION@
Section: admin
Priority: optional
Architecture: @ARCH@
Depends: libc6 (>= 2.35)
Maintainer: Siorb contributors <noreply@github.com>
Homepage: https://github.com/bulengerk/siorb
Vcs-Git: https://github.com/bulengerk/siorb.git
Vcs-Browser: https://github.com/bulengerk/siorb
Rules-Requires-Root: no
Description: offline-first semantic package orchestrator
 Siorb resolves portable logical package intent into an auditable plan for
 native package managers. It does not require a hosted Siorb service.
